The two lovely Frozen Disney princesses need your help today. Elsa and Anna have made out a plan to attend a party tonight, but they do not have any idea what to put on to look fabulous. Do you want to help these Frozen sisters to attain the desired looks? Join Frozen Disney Princess Costume game and prove the world that you have an amazing make-up and fashion sense! You have to dress them up one by one. First give them a proper dress and give them a complete makeover!
Everything you would be displayed on the screen in this brand new dressing game for girls. All you need to go is just check out all the outfit and accessory options to make them look fabulous. Choose your girl and start mixing and matching as many options as you can! Give your first girl an umbrella or a handbag in her hand or a long golden stick! Choose a lovely long gown and pair it with a nice hairstyle and matching jewelry and a pair of suitable sandals!
Once her dressing is done, make sure to apply all the efforts to give her a complete makeover.  Style her up with a soothing eyebrow and use all other beauty items including lipstick, blush, eye shadow and mascara! Also use the contact lenses to make her look gorgeous in this html5 girls game. Hurry up ladies! Your second girl is also waiting for her turn. Do the same for the second girl to help her get an exciting look. Check out more dress-up games that are free to play online, no download required on atmegame.com!
